## Design Decisions

1. **MEU-PH prefix** — continues the `MEU-PW` convention from P2.5b
2. **New MEUs over reopening** — Gap A/F touch files from MEU-78/84 (✅ approved), new MEUs created
3. **09-scheduling.md cross-refs deferred** — minor updates at MEU-PH7 implementation time
4. **Templates GUI deferred to MEU-72** — MCP CRUD provides agent access without GUI
5. **Schema v2 opt-in per policy** — existing v1 policies unchanged; v2 requires explicit declaration
